{"id": 1014, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于收纳，你最大的困扰是什么？", "description": "户型太小，我心太大。（题图来自：Jayde Perkin）", "record_count": 2149, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183812b160AXOkuYcmTn8t.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-28T01:00:22Z", "options": [{"id": 82688, "content": "熟悉的东西陌生化，陌生的东西惊喜出现", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 625552}, {"id": 82944, "content": "收好了东西，发现要拿出来用然后又乱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609429}, {"id": 82689, "content": "带来好心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 625552}, {"id": 82691, "content": "一开始使用时会放回原处，久了以后就开始乱扔", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479392}, {"id": 83206, "content": "发现了新的收纳神器马上就扔掉刚买的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 604937}, {"id": 82695, "content": "收好了下次需要的时候忘记放哪了…还有些永远无法归类的东东。", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624825}, {"id": 82696, "content": "忙的时候乱丢，闲时才慢慢收拾", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 425163}, {"id": 82697, "content": "无法维持", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 574254}, {"id": 82699, "content": "收拾完了转眼就忘记放哪了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615126}, {"id": 83467, "content": "我还没有房子……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628696}, {"id": 88846, "content": "放好的衣服在最下面抽出来上面的全尼玛倒了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219928}, {"id": 115470, "content": "一用就乱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755861}, {"id": 82706, "content": "灰尘多，哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624226}, {"id": 83474, "content": "如何让我老公在拿衣服时不打乱原来的收纳", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597485}, {"id": 82707, "content": "领导每次看到我的桌子都忍不住要骂我", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601008}, {"id": 83219, "content": "东西越收拾越多 还不如不收拾", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273550}, {"id": 82710, "content": "要用的东西等不用的时候就找到了", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573498}, {"id": 82711, "content": "房子太小，大脑太乱", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547590}, {"id": 83225, "content": "不知道如何维持", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589822}, {"id": 82715, "content": "充电线！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168039}, {"id": 91675, "content": " 一边收纳，一边买，东西越来越多，越来越难收纳，还控制不住", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653436}, {"id": 82716, "content": "我只能推荐以上各位使用闲鱼了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419850}, {"id": 82972, "content": "怎么放都不能完全利用空间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540792}, {"id": 82717, "content": "一水儿黑衣服黑裤子全靠摸料子辨别???", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 612075}, {"id": 82718, "content": "我还需要多赚钱啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611598}, {"id": 83742, "content": "收好了就拿不出来了2333", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630419}, {"id": 82719, "content": "断舍离，坚持扔东西……轻生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238914}, {"id": 83232, "content": "放收纳箱了渐渐就忘了有这样东西…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609230}, {"id": 83489, "content": "懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581266}, {"id": 82722, "content": "收了之后就再也找不到了( •̀∀•́ )", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193835m9Eskl5ARhoyzF8B.jpg", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191634}, {"id": 82723, "content": "收了之后就再找不到了( •̀∀•́ )", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191634}, {"id": 82725, "content": "收了就找不到了呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 625778}, {"id": 82728, "content": "你是收纳，不是装进纸箱搬家。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141748}, {"id": 82984, "content": "我喜欢收纳........girls", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 612494}, {"id": 82729, "content": "为什么会乱", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279788}, {"id": 82730, "content": "我有东西可以收吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581516}, {"id": 82731, "content": "收纳完之后再也找不到要用的东西在哪?", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193836fqtOnIDQLmRAjh1S", "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 33674}, {"id": 83243, "content": "地儿太小了！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214486}, {"id": 81965, "content": "煮好菜取下来的锅盖不知道该放哪，非常占地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 81966, "content": "换季的衣服没地方放 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 82734, "content": "陷入不舍得扔越堆越多以及一怒之下都扔了发觉从头开始买买买的死循环中……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239090}, {"id": 82990, "content": "收完了，就找不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 626808}, {"id": 81967, "content": "买回来的收纳工具都没坚持用，最后收纳这些工具本身也占了好多地方。 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 177, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 82991, "content": "越收拾东西越多...", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624527}, {"id": 82736, "content": "妈的收纳箱都卖那么贵，值吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 548345}, {"id": 